citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:45am on
02/18/2016.
VMO Cole and ACI Bartels spoke with the licensee. The licensee was unavailable due to other obligations.
Additional Inspectors
Cole Heather, Supervisory Animal Care Specialist
